AddToMenu RootMenu "Root Menu" Title
+ "&Terminal"         Exec exec urxvt
+ "&Clock"            Exec exec xclock
+ ""                  Nop
+ "&Window Ops"       Popup Window-Ops
+ "&X11 Session"      Popup X11-Session

# Move-Resize x y w h
DestroyFunc Move-Resize
AddToFunc Move-Resize
+ I Move $0 $1
+ I Resize $2 $3
+ I Raise

AddToMenu Window-Ops
+ "&1 Left%icons/pos_left.png%"     Move-Resize 5p    5p   1067p 1025p
+ "&2 Top%icons/pos_top.png%"       Move-Resize 1113p 5p   770p 660p
+ "&3 Bottom%icons/pos_bottom.png%" Move-Resize 1113p 670p 770p 410p
+ ""                                Nop
+ "&4 Minimize%icons/minimize.png%" Iconify
+ "&5 Close%icons/close.png%"       Close

AddToMenu X11-Session
+ "Re&fresh Screen"   Refresh
+ "&Restart WM"       Restart
+ ""                  Nop
+ "Exit to xterm"     Restart xterm
+ "Exit WM"           Quit

